<h1>Aesthetic Clinics in Pattaya: Treatments, Prices and How to Choose <em>Safely</em></h1>
<p class="sub">Botox, fillers, laser and skin treatments in Pattaya — indicative costs and, more importantly, how to pick a licensed, reputable clinic.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">NS</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Naree Suwan</b>
<span>Local contributor · born and raised in Pattaya</span>
