</div>
</div>
<h2 id="prices">Indicative prices for 2026</h2>
<p>Here's the question everyone asks: how much does it cost? Prices below are <strong>indicative ranges</strong> for 2026 and vary by product brand, the doctor's experience, the clinic's location and how much product you actually need. A reputable clinic prices by area or by syringe and tells you the brand before you commit. Be suspicious of prices that look far cheaper than everything else — in injectables, a bargain often means diluted or counterfeit product.</p>
