<h1>Areas to <em>be careful</em> about in Pattaya</h1>
<p class="sub">Pattaya is far safer than its reputation — but a few zones genuinely warrant your attention. This is an honest, lived-in look at which areas to be cautious in, the scams that cluster in each, and simple ways to stay safe, written by a seven-year resident.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">OV</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Olga Vavilova</b>
<span>Olga Vavilova · Senior writer · 7 years living in Pattaya</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
<span class="when">
