<li><a href="#beach-road">Beach Road &amp;amp; Second Road after dark</a></li>
<li><a href="#scams-by-area">Common scams, mapped by area</a></li>
<li><a href="#solo-female">Solo &amp;amp; female travellers</a></li>
<li><a href="#safe-areas">The genuinely calm areas</a></li>
<li><a href="#stay-safe">Simple rules to stay safe</a></li>
<li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
</ol>
