<h1>Bangkok to <em>Pattaya</em>: 6 transport options compared</h1>
<p class="sub">Taxi, public bus, minivan, private transfer, rental and train. Honest cost, honest travel time, honest hassle — tested route by route on the 147 km down Motorway 7 from BKK and DMK airports.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">DR</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Daniel Reyes</b>
<span>Travel editor · 5 years across Chonburi · 200+ Bangkok–Pattaya runs</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
<span class="when">
<svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16 is-muted"><use href="#pg-clock"></use></svg>
            Updated Jun 13, 2026
          </span>
<div class="share-btns">
<button aria-label="Share this article" type="button"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16"><use href="#pg-share"></use></svg></button>
</div>
