<h1>The 8 best <em>beach clubs</em> in Pattaya</h1>
<p class="sub">Pool, music and a sea view, from lazy daytime loungers to sunset DJ sessions. These are the eight beach clubs in Pattaya worth your day — with real entry costs, minimum spends, and an honest line on who each one suits.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">OV</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Olga Vavilova</b>
<span>By Olga Vavilova · Senior writer, 7 years in Pattaya · day-tested every club here as a paying guest</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
<span class="when">
<svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16 is-muted"><use href="#pg-clock"></use></svg>
            Updated Jun 10, 2026
          </span>
<div class="share-btns">
