</div>
</header>
<!-- HERO -->
<figure class="art-hero"><img alt="Beach clubs pattaya 1 – The 8 bestbeach clubsin Pattaya" fetchpriority="high" height="506" loading="eager" src="../Pattaya-Tum-Gorseller-Resized/beach-clubs-pattaya-1.webp" width="1100"/>
      <figcaption class="cap"><span class="lead"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16"><use href="#pg-pin"></use></svg> Beach clubs in Pattaya · pools, sun loungers and sunset DJs from Pratumnak to Jomtien</span><span class="credit">Go To Pattaya</span></figcaption></figure>
<!-- TL;DR -->
<div class="tldr">
<h4><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-20"><use href="#pg-info"></use></svg> If you only have 30 seconds</h4>
<p>For the all-round best <b>beach club in Pattaya</b>, go to <b>Cave Beach Club on Pratumnak</b> — proper sand, a clifftop pool and a ฿0 entry day if you spend on food and drink. For families and a calmer pool day, <b>The Glass House Jomtien</b> wins; for the loudest sunset party, it's <b>Lima Beach Club</b>. Expect a <b>minimum spend of ฿300–800</b> rather than a hard ticket at most of them, ฿1,000+ for a day bed on weekends. Daytime is relaxed and good value; the scene tilts louder and pricier after 4pm.</p>
</div>
</div>
<!-- LAYOUT -->
<div class="art-layout">
<article class="art-body">
<!-- MOBILE STICKY TOC -->
<div class="mtoc">
<details id="mtocDetails">
<summary>
<span class="lbl"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16"><use href="#pg-menu"></use></svg> Table of contents</span>
