<div class="mtoc-bar"><i id="mtocBar"></i></div>
</div>
<p>"Beach club" means something specific in Pattaya, and it isn't the row of plastic chairs and ฿100 deck umbrellas on Beach Road. The real beach clubs — pool, DJ, day beds, a kitchen and a bar with a proper sea view — cluster on <strong>Pratumnak Hill</strong> and along <strong>Jomtien</strong>, away from the main city strip. That's where I've spent more sweaty research afternoons than I'll admit, and it's where the eight clubs below live.</p>
<p>This is a working list of the <strong>best beach clubs in Pattaya</strong> for 2026, ranked by how good a day they actually deliver — not by who shouts loudest on Instagram. I've put real entry and minimum-spend numbers next to each, flagged who each one suits, and been honest about the catches. If you want bars with a view instead of a pool, see our <a class="inline" href="blog-walking-street-guide.html">Walking Street guide</a> or the sibling <a class="inline" href="blog-rooftop-bars-pattaya.html">rooftop bars in Pattaya</a> list.</p>
<h2 id="how-we-picked">How we picked these eight</h2>
<figure class="art-img">
<img alt="Beach clubs pattaya 2 in Pattaya, Thailand" height="428" loading="lazy" src="../Pattaya-Tum-Gorseller-Resized/beach-clubs-pattaya-2.webp" width="760"/>
<figcaption>Beach Clubs Pattaya 2 · The 8 bestbeach clubsin Pattaya</figcaption>
</figure>

<p>I visited each as a normal paying guest — no comped beds, no press invites — on at least one weekday and one weekend so the prices and crowds reflect what you'll actually meet. The ranking weighs five things: the quality of the swim (real sand or a good pool), value (entry versus minimum spend), the vibe at the time of day each does best, food and drink quality, and how easy it is to reach without a car.</p>
<p>Pattaya's beach-club scene changes faster than almost anything else in town — venues rebrand, close for a wet-season refit, or flip from family-friendly by day to a 21+ party by night. Everything here was checked at street level in early 2026, and I've noted where a place runs seasonal hours.</p>
<div class="callout">
<div class="ic"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-20"><use href="#pg-verified"></use></svg></div>
<div><h4>No pay-to-play</h4><p>Nobody pays to appear on this list. Every entry fee, minimum spend and day-bed price below was paid in person in 2026 — the same standard we hold across every <a class="inline" href="plan-my-trip.html">trip-planning guide</a>. If a club drops off next season, it's because the day got worse, not because of money.</p></div>
</div>
<h2 id="the-clubs">The 8 best beach clubs, ranked</h2>
<p>Here's the at-a-glance verdict before the detail. The three quick picks below cover the choices most people are actually deciding between; the full eight follow with prices and honest notes.</p>
<div class="verdict">
<div class="qv">
<div class="qv-label"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16"><use href="#pg-editors-pick"></use></svg> Best all-round</div>
