<p>Olga Vavilova has lived in Pattaya for seven years, splitting her time between a Jomtien condo and Central Pattaya's restaurant scene, and she swims, runs and people-watches across these beaches most weeks. She writes our area and food guides from the sand up, not from a booking site, and nobody pays to appear in her rankings.</p>
</div>
</div>
