<h1>The best <em>beachfront areas in Pattaya</em> to stay</h1>
<p class="sub">Want to wake up to the sea? Not every part of Pattaya delivers that. We rank the best beachfront areas in Pattaya to stay right by the sand — Wong Amat, Jomtien, Pratumnak, Naklua and Beach Road — with what's around each and real 2026 room rates.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">OV</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Olga Vavilova</b>
<span>Olga Vavilova · Senior writer · 7 years living between Jomtien and Wong Amat</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
