<h1>Beachfront or <em>budget hotel</em> in Pattaya: how to choose</h1>
<p class="sub">Pay for the sea view, or save the baht for activities? This is the honest, lived-in take on whether to book a beachfront or budget hotel in Pattaya — with real 2026 room rates, who each genuinely suits, and a clear verdict so you don't over- or under-spend.</p>
